眼鏡凍爛左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"安全套有冇用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cc58f58160699bfe2488f98d6a9d17bf23aa21","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f15f04d006f612662d6d5c95c281aa3da6139fe","tid":1124254,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33ec469e0b0bed09f7a8dfe5204a34ff4620d3b4","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3589e962ddd079cc51fcf14a04064e72465d5eb","tid":1124254,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"使咗幾錢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"頭一個月計埋機票<br />\n西伯利亞-&gt;塞爾維亞 HK$9,000<br />\n之後一個月<br />\n薩拉熱窩-&gt;西維爾 HK$ 11,000<br />\n之後未計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"全程住hostel? 食麵包?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:24:39.000Z","msg":"全程住hostel<br />\n8個人一間房上下隔床<br />\n<br />\n食就唔會太慳，我本身我憎食麵包，我食過2次麵包係因為當地野食黎。<br />\n東歐巴爾幹我食得好好，又牛排又魚乜都有<br />\n重點係你要食當地野，我匈牙利遇到個中國遊客，問我附近有冇中餐廳，咁就唔貴就奇<br />\n<br />\n貴地方就lunch食薯片(歐洲國家薯仔)<br />\n夜晚就買餸自己煮，大魚大肉大雞大芝士意"},{"pid":"1e445715d161053194df085ec216a3d7cb3887e9","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>...<br />\n已經冇用唔同國家既貨幣、車飛<br />\n1500歐元現金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最失敗係我冇帶後備眼鏡<br />\n三個月行程，第二日西伯利亞零下30度，我副眼鏡凍爛左</blockquote>安全套有冇用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個冇帶故意整落去，睇下邊個留心聽書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9361870ad453cead72901a568ced04b3bd9a8ce","tid":1124254,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4cc58f58160699bfe2488f98d6a9d17b