g/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXj6AgWr.jpg&h=52ef2d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wc6wzLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWc6wzLe.jpg&h=c98afc1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fff139fd6ae3ab773fc43d82b5b3d63200988b9","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我大概知有咩準備</blockquote><br />\n我講漏左:<br />\n<br />\n拖鞋<br />\n襪x3<br />\nhostel/快餐店攞既厠紙"},{"pid":"8f8e97c2854eddf5e04a4167685c5256e596455e","tid":1124254,"uid":198175,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"唔駛帶太大的背囊，45L左右就差唔多，太大裝太多嘢會好重，揹住十幾KG周圍行追巴士趕飛機搵旅店好Q辛苦.<br />\n<br />\n去西藏或是落後地方最好帶個睡袋，高原入夜會好凍吓，山旮旯D旅店Ｄ被幾年唔洗好污漕，試過去西藏Kailash轉山喺山上瞓帳篷旅店，雖然有被舖，但冇睡袋係瞓唔到，瞓機場火車站都啱用。<br />\n<br />\nＴ裇底褲同襪要洗完快干同冇臭汗味可以買merino wool, i.e. icebeaker, smartwool,咁你可以帶少好多換洗衣物。<br />\n<br />\n風褸，長褲，鞋都要防水透氣，遇著雨雪天氣時你就知道防水透氣性能係好重要，防水防風先保到䁔。行山鞋唔駛要高筒，得個重字平時又用唔著，如經常去行山帶支行山扙仲實際，Nikko兩三百元好抵玩吓。<br />\n<br />\n去大陸ATM要銀联咭，去歐洲最好係master card cirrus，唔一定要用credit card撳機，credit card好多時淨係得cash advace當你借錢，又要食你3%charge同蝕滙價。<br />\n<br />\n洗浴衛生用品可以去到先買，而家好多hostel都會提供，周圍都有超市同7仔，反而記得帶包紙巾，急起上嚟冇紙用時方後悔。<br />\n<br />\n阿叔12年前去中東，由以色列陸路玩到拉薩玩咗3個幾月，個背囊只得35L，外掛一個睡袋，嗰時仲未興merino wool，要成日搵洗衣舖洗衫好on9，<a href=\"http://仲要當年冇得手機上網冇booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%B2%E8%A6%81%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%87%E5%BE%97%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2%E5%86%87booking.com&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=eb204971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">仲要當年冇得手機上網冇booking.com</a>冇google map，要帶本LP磚頭當聖經，當然仲會帶返一兩本書去解悶啦，邊似而家一部iphone搞掂晒！"},{"pid":"4c8639290223c371b56e1bdf537083ab4555a5f8","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fff139fd6ae3ab773fc43d82b5b3d63200988b9","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我大概知有咩準備</blockquote><br />\n我講漏左:<br />\n<br />\n拖鞋<br />\n襪x3<br />\nhostel/快餐店攞既厠紙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"AV幾套入定手機"},{"pid":"e346987531f58f0e83d250b418a012bfdaad0bc5","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔駛帶太大的背囊，45L左右就差唔多....一兩本書去解悶啦，邊似而家一部iphone搞掂晒！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講完我至醒起軟件野<br />\n<a href=\"http://agoda.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fagoda.com&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=8c20a316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">agoda.com</a><br />\nairbnb<br />\nbusradar<br />\ngoogle trip <br />\ntripadvisor<br />\n<a href=\"http://freetour.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffreetour.com&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=a75533c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">freetour.com</a>睇下邊個點有得join free tour<br />\nGoogle drive/其他雲端 (必要時比錢加容量)<br />\nAV x4<br />\n銀行開海外提款<br />\noffline game x2<br />\ngoogle keep寫遊記所見所聞<br />\nLightroom CC執相<br />\ngoogle pay"},{"pid":"2469cb821023d7a671b04f53893c4546dfbfd70a","tid":1124254,"uid":223079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"- 大背囊<br />\n- 小背包（day trip用）<br />\n- 頂到4-5日的內衣褲襪<br />\n- 外衣兩三件、老牛2條、短褲兩件<br />\n- 雨絨一件<br />\n- 梳洗kit(牙膏洗面膏剃鬚防曬產品etc)<br />\n- 洗面巾沖涼巾<br />\n- 太陽眼鏡、後備眼鏡（一定要！）<br />\n- 手機（最好兩部，而且影完相upload去google photo)用不用單反自己選擇，無可無不可<br />\n- 錢<br />\n- 兩張atm cars<br />\n- 一張信用卡<br />\n- 內腰包裝錢同卡<br />\n- 護照<br />\n- 身分證<br />\n- 回鄉卡<br />\n- travel health kit(退燒藥止痾藥etc）問醫生買<br />\n- 旅遊保險 旅遊保險 旅遊保險（一定要有！唔好慳）<br />\n- 上網卡<br />\n- 行山鞋，波鞋，拖鞋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得差不多，太多嘢就難manage.<br />\n如果要露營自備營具，我唔興所以唔識太多....<br />\n<br />\n每個計劃所到國家的簽證知識（要不要簽證費，每次簽證要預海關問你stay 喺邊間hostel etc)"},{"pid":"c956cd6a15c64e907ba776d6c74021446bb30571","tid":1124254,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"真心唔需要準備<br />\n要用自然有方法"},{"pid":"17472d7c8eb600d63c6b050799c517b26c570dfc","tid":1124254,"uid":223079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:32:14.000Z","msg":"我覺得普通鞋可以了<br />\n<br />\n我去百內國家公園行一日百內塔同EL Chalten的Fitz Roy(總之係行山la...)都只是著穿咗窿的Nike air行都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />....<br />\n<br />\n要支行山杖反而緊要好多...去淘寶買啦"},{"pid":"dafdfa3a91a98c91269ca4400697ce78d085c567","tid":1124254,"uid":223079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c956cd6a15c64e907ba776d6c74021446bb30571","tid":1124254,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"真心唔需要準備<br />\n要用自然有方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:33:07.000Z","msg":"神覆！同意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5d8d900ba60638e8d57afe51df7c1a5773d86b","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c956cd6a15c64e907ba776d6c74021446bb30571","tid":1124254,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"真心唔需要準備<br />\n要用自然有方法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:48:35.000Z","msg":"最後怕你比錢比到你肉痛咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3be6a3e565f1659c516bffa0ca6b9d145175be","tid":1124254,"uid":215011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed5d8d900ba60638e8d57afe51df7c1a5773d86b","tid":1124254,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c956cd6a15c64e907ba776d6c74021446bb30571","tid":1124254,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"真心唔需要準備<br />\n要用自然有方法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:48:35.000Z","msg":"最後怕你比錢比到你肉痛咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-